==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[normal]] [[subgroup]]''' (''plural'' '''normal subgroups''')

#{{grouptheory}} A subgroup ''H'' of a group ''G'' that is [[invariant]] under [[conjugation]]; that is, for all elements ''h'' of ''H'' and for all elements ''g'' in ''G'', the element ''gng''<sup>−1</sup> is in ''H''.

